===message:I really liked the point you made as well. In my response I called the Federalists visionaries, because they realized that in order to move forward and become the great nation that we have become, they would have to be organized and unified.  The creation of centralized government served not only the purpose intended, but in addition as you stated strengthened us both internally and externally from future attacks by Great Britain and other countries.
